    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/f201ae767b3a728f520e780c5bab0d24.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=264 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/fb55cd71266d968342b43d842f0a4a81.webp?t=1701702083\" width=499 height=20 /></span><br>什么是 Conclave 虚拟桌面游戏？<br><br>Conclave 是将你的 TTRPG 活动推向新高度的简单直观方式，无论你的团队是在同一房间内还是散布在各个领域中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/b78652904bc74105a0ffdf5f19408065.poster.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/b78652904bc74105a0ffdf5f19408065.webm?t=1701702083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Conclave 强调的是体验，而不是数字。无需管理统计数据或费力研究复杂的菜单；我们假设你已经掌握了角色卡。相反，我们旨在提供一个可自定义的空间，配备了简单明了的工具，供你建立和进行游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/e3ab76100b00e0c1ca8cae888a199c18.webp?t=1701702083\" width=204 height=20 /></span><br>技能<br><br>Conclave 提供一系列工具，帮助你在游戏旅程中获得成功，包括骰子、测量工具、状态效果以及雾化绘画系统。我们提供了一些资源，帮助你入门，但这是你的游戏，你的故事。我们有何权利决定其中包含了什么呢？你可以快速简单地导入你会话所需的一切：地图、代币、肖像，甚至 3D 迷你模型！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/27acc384ce4c5bb557caea818ba5614f.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=349 /></span><br>Conclave 支持 Hero Forge® 访问密钥，这意味着你可以连接你的账户，解锁你的定制数字迷你图书馆。当你连接你的账户时，你将解锁 5 个免费迷你图！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/e99ea68a7b0734d668443190f90ee673.poster.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/e99ea68a7b0734d668443190f90ee673.webm?t=1701702083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>改变白天时间、光线，甚至天气和自然效果，以获得你想要的氛围。Conclave 的极简设计意味着当你需要的时候它会退出，这样玩家可以专注于你们共同创建的故事和体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/ff10cd2238905b15ddafb476e1e78257.webp?t=1701702083\" width=401 height=20 /></span><br>协同叙事<br><br>Conclave 的目标不仅在于复制经典桌面游戏的体验，还在于提升它，使团队汇聚更容易。Conclave 主要针对本地多人游戏设计，因此在同一房间内的玩家可以轻松传递一个或两个控制器。在线玩家无需担心，Conclave 完全支持 Steam 的远程协同游戏功能。只需一份 Conclave 副本，整个团队都可以一起玩耍和创造。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/53114e5196de6e8f4235e2aa70a49cb6.poster.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/53114e5196de6e8f4235e2aa70a49cb6.webm?t=1701702083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/ed5981d9e2624763f846baa6aa417d3a.webp?t=1701702083\" width=185 height=20 /></span><br>自制规则<br><br>Conclave 主要用于促进桌面角色扮演游戏，但没有规定说你不能扩展。如果涉及在棋盘上移动棋子，那很可能可以在 Conclave 中进行游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/5643bbe088585ae7cccd1e37f58cb80d.poster.avif?t=1701702083\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2373800/extras/5643bbe088585ae7cccd1e37f58cb80d.webm?t=1701702083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>我们邀请你加入我们不断增长的 Discord 社区，你可以在那里寻找团队、讨论你的活动，或者仅仅与我们聊天。我们期待成为你下一个冒险的一部分。",
